<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.186509>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 − 20. 9 − 14. Boonea seminuda. 9. holotype (MCZ 186052); 10 − 14 (MNRJ 10956); 9 − 11. whole shells (lengths: 9: 3.81 mm; 10: 4.0 mm; 11: 1.8 mm); 12. last whorl; 13 − 14: protoconchs. Scale bars: 200 Μm. 15 − 20. Boonea scymnocelata: 15, 17, 19 − 20. holotype (MZSP 89107); 16, 18. paratype (MZSP 89108); 15 − 16: whole shells (lengths: 15: 2.0 mm; 16: 2.0 mm); 17 − 19: protoconchs; 20: last whorl. Scale bars: 200 Μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/186509/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

